    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a practical daily commuter. The engine and transmission are functioning well, and it has been recently serviced to ensure mechanical stability. However, the exterior shows visible signs of its age, including some minor scratches, small dents, and fading paint in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear, and while all essential electronics work, some interior trim pieces are loose. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
