    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that's full of character! This car has been well-loved and shows some honest signs of its journey on the road, but it remains a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, functional vehicle. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a trustworthy ride that\u2019s ready to take on many more miles with you!",
