      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit showcases a flawless exterior and an interior that remains in showroom state. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers an unparalleled driving experience for the most sophisticated collector. A rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar preserved in its most optimal form.",
